## 1. PROJECT OVERVIEW

**RepairMyBike** is a hyperlocal B2B + B2C service platform for two-wheeler (motorcycle/scooter) repairs and spare parts e-commerce. It includes:
- Customer booking (home/shop visits, emergency quick service)
- Spare parts e-commerce with cart/orders
- Subscription plans (Basic/Premium, tiered visits)
- Mechanic/staff management & assignment
- Admin real-time operations dashboard
- Payments via Razorpay, loyalty points, referral bonuses
- Push notifications via Firebase FCM

